dct_title_s: Map of Queensland to accompany the Commissioner for Railways report for 1905-06
dct_description_sm: Prepared for the Commissioner for Railways at the Chief Engineers Office Brisbane 30.6.1906 ; By Authority G.A. Vaughan, Govt. Printer, Brisbane ; C.P.
Shows railways (including under construction, approved by parliament, private lines), towns, stations, distribution of cattle & sheep, waterways, Great Barrier Reef.
Statistics (for Decr. 31st, 1905) for population, cattle and sheep stock return
"Issued with the 'Year Book of Queensland' and the 'Year Book of Australia.'"
